            "title": "大埔豪宅遇竊  損失點算中",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"大埔淺月灣二期發生爆竊案。劉漢權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6c72e78671403725d5ce2f58680f5d58/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022009173371218.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">大埔淺月灣二期發生爆竊案。劉漢權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（20日）晨7時許，大埔淺月灣二期一單位戶主發現屋內有搜掠痕跡，懷疑遭賊人爆竊，於是報警，警方到場調查，翻看閉路電視，相信賊人從花園門口潛入犯案，損失仍待點算中。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091947/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔淺月灣二期發生爆竊案。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d61d0819bfe186341b084b7e74701f95/2025-02/01_21.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔淺月灣二期發生爆竊案。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091948/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔淺月灣二期發生爆竊案。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4bd522982291176ea460bb2794dbbe8/2025-02/02_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔淺月灣二期發生爆竊案。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
